messages.messageBody:
I've had a request for a topic chat. This will probably be saved and
added to the webpage, because there's not much about these things
there right now.

Thanks!
Sandra


What about young children who are expressing themselves physically by
pushing or hitting or biting? Many of us have seen it, felt it,
helped kids through. If you have any ideas, please come and share.
If you want to bring links to things you've already written or that
you've read and liked, I'll collect and save them so they'll be
available in the future.

Please forward this on to anyone you think might need it or be
particularly good at helping others about it.

Thanks!
